item.title: CVE-2020-4717|2024-08-04T08:14:57.482Z -- ibm -- spss%20modeler
item.description: A vulnerability exists in IBM SPSS Modeler Subscription Installer that allows a user with create symbolic link permission to write arbitrary file in another protected path during product installation. IBM X-Force ID: 187727.
